vantaging the resistance</em></li><li><em>Best power and torque performance especially at low speeds in cross models</em></li><li><em>Strong power delivery in enduro versions. The best for the track.</em></li><li><em>Intense sound for an extreme use of the product</em></li><li><em>Homologated product in compliance with the European provisions. It respects FIM provisions for competition use.</em></li><li><em>Huge weight reduction unlike the original model and easier driving of the bike</em></li><li><em>Highly qualified experience gained in the off-road competition world.</em></li><li><em>Reliability of one of the best world producers of motorbike exhaust systems.</em></li></ul><p><em><br></em></p></b></div> </p> <p> 	 </p> </div> <p align="center"> </p> <p align="center"><IMG border=0  src="http://srv1.anotherbike.com/mivv/img/spedizioneuk.jpg"></p> <p align="center"> </p> <br><br><br></TD> </TR> </table>
