G border=0 src="http://srv1.anotherbike.com/mivv/img/dot_clear.gif"><br><img src="http://srv1.anotherbike.com/mivv/img/alllanguages/XHO0002L7_d.jpg" /><br><IMG border=0 src="http://srv1.anotherbike.com/mivv/img/dot_clear.gif"><br><IMG border=0 src="http://srv1.anotherbike.com/mivv/img/dot_clear.gif"><br><img src="http://srv1.anotherbike.com/mivv/img/alllanguages/XHO0002L7_e.jpg" /><br><IMG border=0 src="http://srv1.anotherbike.com/mivv/img/dot_clear.gif"><br><IMG border=0 src="http://srv1.anotherbike.com/mivv/img/dot_clear.gif"><br><img src="http://srv1.anotherbike.com/mivv/img/alllanguages/XHO0002_SUONO_sc.jpg" /><br><IMG border=0 src="http://srv1.anotherbike.com/mivv/img/dot_clear.gif"><br><IMG border=0 src="http://srv1.anotherbike.com/mivv/img/dot_clear.gif"><br><img src="http://srv1.anotherbike.com/mivv/img/alllanguages/XHO0002_POWER_STEEL_sc.jpg" /><br><IMG border=0 src="http://srv1.anotherbike.com/mivv/img/dot_clear.gif"><br><IMG border=0 src="http://srv1.anotherbike.com/mivv/img/dot_clear.gif"><br><img src="http://srv1.anotherbike.com/mivv/img/alllanguages/XHO0002L7_SUONO_dy.jpg" /><br><IMG border=0 src="http://srv1.anotherbike.com/mivv/img/dot_clear.gif"><br><IMG border=0 src="http://srv1.anotherbike.com/mivv/img/dot_clear.gif"><br><img src="http://srv1.anotherbike.com/mivv/img/alllanguages/XHO0002L7_dy.jpg" /><br><IMG border=0 src="http://srv1.anotherbike.com/mivv/img/dot_clear.gif"><br><IMG border=0 src="http://srv1.anotherbike.com/mivv/img/dot_clear.gif"><br><img src="http://srv1.anotherbike.com/mivv/img/alllanguages/XHO0002L7_maxpower_dy.jpg" /><br><IMG border=0 src="http://srv1.anotherbike.com/mivv/img/dot_clear.gif"><br><IMG border=0 src="http://srv1.anotherbike.com/mivv/img/dot_clear.gif"><br><img src="http://srv1.anotherbike.com/mivv/img/alllanguages/XHO0002L7_maxtorque_dy.jpg" /></p> <div style="margin:0px 10px 0px 10px;font-size:18px; color:#FFFFFF;"> <p><div class="box_titolo"><font color="#ff0010" size="5">Full systems for race and road use</font