<p>If you are aware that there will be a delay in us receiving payment please contact us on the above number or email <a href="mailto:sales@ukgooddeals.com">sales@ukgooddeals.com</a> to let us know and we will place your order on hold for up to five days.</p>
<p><strong>What payment methods are available?</strong></p>
