<p>We accept payments via most major credit/debit cards (excluding American Express) via our secure online ordering system or over the telephone by calling 01772 792600, where are customer service team will be happy to help. Please note that for security reasons we will only dispatch items to the cardholder&rsquo;s registered address.<br />
