<p>We accept direct cash deposit or bank transfer as a payment option. We can post purchased items to any address if you are using this payment option.<br />
When making payment through bank transfer please call us or e-mail us to let us know you will be paying via this option, informing us if possible of when you expect payment to be made.</p>
